msgctxt "talk_06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>When you get to be my age, you start\n"
"reminiscing about all the memories\n"
"from your childhood.\n"
"Heh, to be honest, growing up out in the\n"
"middle of nowhere... Well, there weren't\n"
"really other kids around.\n"
"<2.so>My only friends were <3.se_co>Harry <4.re_co>and "
"<5.se_co>Mary<6.re_co>.<7.pa>\n"
"I remember playing with <8.se_co>Harry <9.re_co>out in\n"
"the maze <10.pa>and <11.se_co>Mary <12.re_co>out by the ruins...<13.ch>"
msgstr ""

