msgctxt "talk_07"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Maybe you've seen the big canyon to\n"
"the southeast.<2.pa> There are some secret\n"
"ruins down at the base of that valley.\n"
"I don't know who built them or when.\n"
"The adults always said not to go near.\n"
"They said it was too dangerous there.\n"
"One day <3.se_co>Mary <4.re_co>and I went out there to\n"
"explore and search for the ruins.\n"
"\n"
"<5.so>In the blink of an eye, <6.se_co>Mary<7.re_co> lost her\n"
"footing. She slipped and tumbled down\n"
"the cliff. <8.pa>I...<9.pa>I never saw her again.\n"
"Sometimes a child's innocent curiosity\n"
"can cause tragedies that can never be\n"
"taken back.\n"
"<10.so>That memory <11.pa>will haunt me until my\n"
"dying day..."
msgstr ""

